data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom and 2 1/2  bath home in the desirable Hidden Lakes development located in the Washington Twp School District. This fantastic home is move-in ready and boasts a fantastic layout for hosting family gatherings.  It has a spacious kitchen with granite countertops. The laundry room and powder room  are both on the first floor. Host memorable dinners and gatherings in the formal dining room, creating cherished memories with loved ones. The nicely sized family room boasts a wood burning fireplace for those cold winter evenings.  Upstairs has 4 generously sized bedrooms  and two full baths.  There is a fantastic backyard with an oversized concrete patio for entertaining.  The back yard is fenced in with a nice 6 foot  white vinyl fence. It is conveniently situated to major highways, shopping & dining. You're also close to Philadelphia and the Jersey shore. This home will not disappoint and where you can call home for years to come. Contact us today for a private tour.
